NEURAL_DE

NEURAL_DE This library offers neuralde methods to help proving ownership on the machine learning models you train.

NEURAL_DE is an initiative under Confiance.ai, an organization dedicated to fostering transparency, fairness, and trust in the field of artificial intelligence.
